      "settings": {
        "kicker": "About Davines",
        "title": "",
        "text": "<h1>Davines</h1><p>“BY CREATING <em>BEAUTY SUSTAINABLY,</em> WE ENCOURAGE PEOPLE TO TAKE CARE OF THEMSELVES, OF THE ENVIRONMENT IN WHICH THEY LIVE & WORK, AND OF THE THINGS THEY LOVE.” -<em>Davide Bollati, President</em><br/></p><p>Davines shampoos, conditioners, hair masks, and treatments are <strong>paraben- and sulfate-free</strong>, made with ingredients of <strong>natural origin</strong>, and sourced from organic farms.</p><p>Davines not only creates products that are on the cutting edge of research for treating dandruff or thinning, damaged, or frizzy hair, but also ensures that its products and packaging have the least impact on the environment through the use of <strong>natural ingredients, eco-friendly packaging & 100% renewable energy</strong>.</p>",
